While in his [[Jinchūriki Forms#Initial Jinchūriki Form|initial jinchūriki form]], Naruto delivers a series of punches to the opponent before uppercutting them into the air. There, Naruto punches the enemy to the ground and delivers a series of punches before kicking the enemy aside.
